hwFrMIB.name: hwFrMIB
hwFrMIB.contactinfo: Huawei Industrial Base Bantian, Longgang Shenzhen 518129 People's Republic of China Website: http://www.huawei.com Email: support@huawei.com
hwFrMIB.description: This MIB is mainly used to indicate the information of Fr interface

hwFrTable.name: hwFrTable
hwFrTable.description: This table is used to indicate the parameters of the Fr interface. The index of this table is hwFrIfIndex.

hwFrEntry.name: hwFrEntry
hwFrEntry.description: This table is used to indicate the parameters of the Fr interface. The index of this entry is hwFrIfIndex.

hwFrEncapType.name: hwFrEncapType
hwFrEncapType.description: Indicates the interface fr encapsulation type. Options: 1.nonstandard(1) - nonstandard encapsulation 2.ietf(2) - RFC1490 encapsulation

hwFrIfType.name: hwFrIfType
hwFrIfType.description: Indicates fr interface type. Options: 1.dte(1) - DTE type 2.dce(2) - DCE type 3.nni(3) - NNI type

hwFrLmiType.name: hwFrLmiType
hwFrLmiType.description: Indicates the Lmi protocol type. Options: 1.notset(1) - NotSet 2.nonstandard(2) - nonstandard type 3.ansi(3) - ANSI type 4.q933a(4) - Q.933a type

hwFrLmiN391DteValue.name: hwFrLmiN391DteValue
hwFrLmiN391DteValue.description: Indicates the parameter of DTE N391. Get 65535 when the fr interface type is DCE. Range: 1-255 Default: 6 Unit: count

hwFrLmiN392DteValue.name: hwFrLmiN392DteValue
hwFrLmiN392DteValue.description: Indicates the parameter of DTE N392. Get 65535 when the fr interface type is DCE. Range: 1-10 Default: 3 Unit: count

hwFrLmiN392DceValue.name: hwFrLmiN392DceValue
hwFrLmiN392DceValue.description: Indicates the parameter of DCE N392. Get 65535 when the fr interface type is DTE. Range: 1-10 Default: 3 Unit: count

hwFrLmiN393DteValue.name: hwFrLmiN393DteValue
hwFrLmiN393DteValue.description: Indicates the parameter of DTE N393. Get 65535 when the fr interface type is DCE. Range: 1-10 Default: 4 Unit: count

hwFrLmiN393DceValue.name: hwFrLmiN393DceValue
hwFrLmiN393DceValue.description: Indicates the parameter of DCE N393. Get 65535 when the fr interface type is DTE. Range: 1-10 Default: 4 Unit: count

hwFrLmiT391DteValue.name: hwFrLmiT391DteValue
hwFrLmiT391DteValue.description: Indicates the parameter of DTE T391. Get 65535 when the fr interface type is DCE. Range: 1-32767 Default: 10 Unit: second

hwFrLmiT392DceValue.name: hwFrLmiT392DceValue
hwFrLmiT392DceValue.description: Indicates the parameter of DCE T392. Get 65535 when the fr interface type is DTE. Range: 5-30 Default: 15 Unit: second

hwFrIphcEnable.name: hwFrIphcEnable
hwFrIphcEnable.description: Indicates IPHC is enabled or disabled. By default, RTP header compression with IPHC format is disabled. true: enable RTP header compression with IPHC format. false: disable RTP header compression with IPHC format.

hwFrIphcNonstandardFormat.name: hwFrIphcNonstandardFormat
hwFrIphcNonstandardFormat.description: Indicates nonstandard-format compressing is enabled or disabled. By default, don't support nonstandard-format while compressing. true: support nonstandard-format while compressing. false: don't support nonstandard-format while compressing.

hwFrIphcTcpInclude.name: hwFrIphcTcpInclude
hwFrIphcTcpInclude.description: Indicates TCP header compression is enabled or disabled. By default, exclude TCP header compression while compressing RTP. true: include TCP header compression while compressing RTP. false: exclude TCP header compression while compressing RTP.

hwFrInarpEnable.name: hwFrInarpEnable
hwFrInarpEnable.description: Indicates inverse address resolution protocol is enabled or disabled. By default, inverse address resolution protocol is enabled. true: inverse address resolution protocol is enabled. false: inverse address resolution protocol is disabled.

hwFrIphcTcpConnection.name: hwFrIphcTcpConnection
hwFrIphcTcpConnection.description: Indicates the number of tcp compression connections. 256 is a valid connection number, get 256 when IPHC is enabled. Get 65535 when IPHC is disabled. Range: 3-255 Default: 256 Unit: count

hwFrIphcRtpConnection.name: hwFrIphcRtpConnection
hwFrIphcRtpConnection.description: Indicates the number of rtp compression connections. 256 is a valid connection number, get 256 when IPHC is enabled. Get 65535 when IPHC is disabled. Range: 3-255 Default: 256 Unit: count

hwFrPvcTable.name: hwFrPvcTable
hwFrPvcTable.description: This table is used to indicate the PVC for the Fr interface. The index of this table are hwFrPvcIfIndex and hwFrPvcDlciNumber.

hwFrPvcEntry.name: hwFrPvcEntry
hwFrPvcEntry.description: This table is used to indicate the PVC for the Fr interface. The index of this entry are hwFrPvcIfIndex and hwFrPvcDlciNumber.

hwFrPvcState.name: hwFrPvcState
hwFrPvcState.description: Indicates the state of the PVC. Options: 1.inactive(1) - inactive 2.active(2) - active

hwFrPvcInarpEnable.name: hwFrPvcInarpEnable
hwFrPvcInarpEnable.description: Indicates the inarp is enabled or disabled. By default, the inarp of the PVC is enabled. true: enable inarp. false: disable inarp.

hwFrPvcGroupTable.name: hwFrPvcGroupTable
hwFrPvcGroupTable.description: This table is used to indicate the pvc-group on the interface. The index of this table are hwFrPvcGroupIfIndex and hwFrPvcGroupName.

hwFrPvcGroupEntry.name: hwFrPvcGroupEntry
hwFrPvcGroupEntry.description: This table is used to indicate the pvc-group on the interface. The index of this entry are hwFrPvcGroupIfIndex and hwFrPvcGroupName.

hwFrPvcGroupName.name: hwFrPvcGroupName
hwFrPvcGroupName.description: Indicates the name of the pvc-group. The name is a string of 1 to 16 characters. Only support visible characters.

hwFrPvcGroupState.name: hwFrPvcGroupState
hwFrPvcGroupState.description: Indicates the state of a pvc-group. Options: 1.inactive(1) - inactive 2.active(2) - active

hwFrPvcGroupTosType.name: hwFrPvcGroupTosType
hwFrPvcGroupTosType.description: Indicates the TOS type of a pvc-group. Options: 1.none(1) - none 2.precedence(2) - precedence 3.dscp(3) - DSCP

hwFrPvcGroupInArpEnable.name: hwFrPvcGroupInArpEnable
hwFrPvcGroupInArpEnable.description: Indicates inarp is enabled or disabled. By default, the inarp of the pvc-group is enabled. true: enable inarp. false: disable inarp.

hwFrPvcGroupMemTable.name: hwFrPvcGroupMemTable
hwFrPvcGroupMemTable.description: This table is used to indicate the member of the pvc-group. The index of this table are hwFrPvcGroupMemIfIndex, hwFrPvcGroupMemPvcGroupName and hwFrPvcGroupMemDlciNumber.

hwFrPvcGroupMemEntry.name: hwFrPvcGroupMemEntry
hwFrPvcGroupMemEntry.description: This table is used to indicate the member of the pvc-group. The index of this entry are hwFrPvcGroupMemIfIndex, hwFrPvcGroupMemPvcGroupName and hwFrPvcGroupMemDlciNumber.

hwFrPvcGroupMemPvcGroupName.name: hwFrPvcGroupMemPvcGroupName
hwFrPvcGroupMemPvcGroupName.description: Indicates the name of the pvc-group. The name is a string of 1 to 16 characters. Only support visible characters.

hwFrPvcGroupMemDlciNumber.name: hwFrPvcGroupMemDlciNumber
hwFrPvcGroupMemDlciNumber.description: Indicates the DLCI of the PVC.

hwFrPvcGroupMemTosType.name: hwFrPvcGroupMemTosType
hwFrPvcGroupMemTosType.description: Indicates the TOS type of a PVC belong to the pvc-group. Options: 1.none(1) - none 2.precedence(2) - precedence 3.dscp(3) - DSCP

hwFrPvcGroupMemDefault.name: hwFrPvcGroupMemDefault
hwFrPvcGroupMemDefault.description: Indicates the TOS value of the PVC whether is default or not. true: default TOS value. false: none default TOS value.

hwFrPvcGroupMemMinGrade.name: hwFrPvcGroupMemMinGrade
hwFrPvcGroupMemMinGrade.description: Indicates the minimum value of the TOS with one member PVC. If the TOS type is precedence, the maximum value cannot be larger than 7. Get 255 when this value is not configed.

hwFrPvcGroupMemMaxGrade.name: hwFrPvcGroupMemMaxGrade
hwFrPvcGroupMemMaxGrade.description: Indicates the maximum value of the TOS with one member PVC. If the TOS type is precedence, the maximum value cannot be larger than 7. Get 255 when this value is not configed.

hwFrPvcGroupMapIpTable.name: hwFrPvcGroupMapIpTable
hwFrPvcGroupMapIpTable.description: This table is used to indicate the bridge mapping on the pvc-group. The index of this table are hwFrPvcGroupMapIpIfIndex, hwFrPvcGroupMapIpName and hwFrPvcGroupMapIpIpAddr.

hwFrPvcGroupMapIpEntry.name: hwFrPvcGroupMapIpEntry
hwFrPvcGroupMapIpEntry.description: This table is used to indicate the bridge mapping on the pvc-group. The index of this entry are hwFrPvcGroupMapIpIfIndex, hwFrPvcGroupMapIpName and hwFrPvcGroupMapIpIpAddr.

hwFrPvcGroupMapIpName.name: hwFrPvcGroupMapIpName
hwFrPvcGroupMapIpName.description: Indicates the name of the pvc-group. The name is a string of 1 to 16 characters.

hwFrPvcGroupMapIpIpAddr.name: hwFrPvcGroupMapIpIpAddr
hwFrPvcGroupMapIpIpAddr.description: Indicates the peer IP address mapped to the pvc-group. Get 0.0.0.0 when the map is default map.

hwFrPvcGroupMapIpMask.name: hwFrPvcGroupMapIpMask
hwFrPvcGroupMapIpMask.description: Indicates the IP address mask mapped to the pvc-group. Get 255.255.255.255 when the map is default map.

hwFrPvcGroupMapIpEncapType.name: hwFrPvcGroupMapIpEncapType
hwFrPvcGroupMapIpEncapType.description: Indicates the encapsulation type of the PVC mapped by pvc-group. 1.nonstandard(1) - nonstandard encapsulation 2.ietf(2) - RFC1490 encapsulation

hwFrPvcGroupMapIpBroadcast.name: hwFrPvcGroupMapIpBroadcast
hwFrPvcGroupMapIpBroadcast.description: Indicates sending broadcast packets is enabled or disabled. By default, sending broadcast packets is disabled. true: enable sending broadcast packets. false: disable sending broadcast packets.

hwFrPvcGroupMapIpDefault.name: hwFrPvcGroupMapIpDefault
hwFrPvcGroupMapIpDefault.description: Indicates the map is default map or not. By default, the map is not default map. true: the map is default map. false: the map is not default map.

hwFrMapIpTable.name: hwFrMapIpTable
hwFrMapIpTable.description: This table is used to indicate the static address mapping for a PVC. The index of this table are hwFrMapIpIfIndex, hwFrMapIpDlciNumber and hwFrMapIpAddress.

hwFrMapIpEntry.name: hwFrMapIpEntry
hwFrMapIpEntry.description: This table is used to indicate the static address mapping for a PVC. The index of this entry are hwFrMapIpIfIndex, hwFrMapIpDlciNumber and hwFrMapIpAddress.

hwFrMapIpAddress.name: hwFrMapIpAddress
hwFrMapIpAddress.description: Indicates the peer IP address mapped to the PVC. Get 0.0.0.0 when the map is default map.

hwFrMapIpMask.name: hwFrMapIpMask
hwFrMapIpMask.description: Indicates the IP address mask. Get 255.255.255.255 when the map is default map.

hwFrMapIpBroadcast.name: hwFrMapIpBroadcast
hwFrMapIpBroadcast.description: Indicates sending broadcast packets is enabled or disabled. By default, sending broadcast packets is disabled. true: enable sending broadcast packets. false: disable sending broadcast packets.

hwFrMapIpEncapType.name: hwFrMapIpEncapType
hwFrMapIpEncapType.description: Indicates the encapsulation type of map. Option: 1.nonstandard(1) - nonstandard encapsulation 2.ietf(2) - RFC1490 encapsulation

hwFrMapIpDefault.name: hwFrMapIpDefault
hwFrMapIpDefault.description: Indicates the map is default map or not. By default, the map is not default map. true: the map is default map. false: the map is not default map.

hwFrMapIpFrf9Enable.name: hwFrMapIpFrf9Enable
hwFrMapIpFrf9Enable.description: Indicates frf9 on the map is enabled or disabled. By default, payload data compression is disabled. true: enable payload data compression. false: disable payload data compression.

hwFrMapIpIphcEnable.name: hwFrMapIpIphcEnable
hwFrMapIpIphcEnable.description: Indicates iphc on the map is enabled or disabled. By default, compress IP/UDP/RTP head with iphc-compression is disabled. true: enable compress IP/UDP/RTP head with iphc-compression. false: disable compress IP/UDP/RTP head with iphc-compression.

hwFrMapIpRtpConnNumber.name: hwFrMapIpRtpConnNumber
hwFrMapIpRtpConnNumber.description: Indicates the number of rtp compression connections. Get 65535 when IPHC is disabled. Range: 3-256 Default: 65535 Unit: count

hwFrMapPppTable.name: hwFrMapPppTable
hwFrMapPppTable.description: This table is used to indicate the PPPoFR mapping on the PVC. The index of this table are hwFrMapPppIfIndex and hwFrMapPppDlciNumber.

hwFrMapPppEntry.name: hwFrMapPppEntry
hwFrMapPppEntry.description: This table is used to indicate the PPPoFR mapping on the PVC. The index of this entry are hwFrMapPppIfIndex and hwFrMapPppDlciNumber.

hwFrMapPppDlciNumber.name: hwFrMapPppDlciNumber
hwFrMapPppDlciNumber.description: Indicates the DLCI of the PVC mapped by PPP.

hwFrMapPppVTIfIndex.name: hwFrMapPppVTIfIndex
hwFrMapPppVTIfIndex.description: Indicates the index of the VT interface.

hwFrMapPppState.name: hwFrMapPppState
hwFrMapPppState.description: Indicates the state of the PPP map. Options: 1.inactive(1) - inactive 2.active(2) - active

hwFrMapBridgeTable.name: hwFrMapBridgeTable
hwFrMapBridgeTable.description: This table is used to indicate the bridge mapping on the PVC. The index of this table are hwFrMapBridgeIfIndex and hwFrMapBridgeDlciNumber.

hwFrMapBridgeEntry.name: hwFrMapBridgeEntry
hwFrMapBridgeEntry.description: This table is used to indicate the bridge mapping on the PVC. The index of this entry are hwFrMapBridgeIfIndex and hwFrMapBridgeDlciNumber.

hwFrMapBridgeDlciNumber.name: hwFrMapBridgeDlciNumber
hwFrMapBridgeDlciNumber.description: Indicates the DLCI of the PVC mapped by bridge.

hwFrMapBridgeState.name: hwFrMapBridgeState
hwFrMapBridgeState.description: Indicates the state of the PVC mapped by bridge. Options: 1.inactive(1) - inactive 2.active(2) - active

hwFrCompliance.name: hwFrCompliance
hwFrCompliance.description: The compliance statement for systems supporting the HUAWEI-Fr-MIB.

hwFrPvcGroupMemObjectGroup.name: hwFrPvcGroupMemObjectGroup
hwFrPvcGroupMemObjectGroup.description: The fr pvc-group member attribute group.

hwFrPvcGroupMapIpObjectGroup.name: hwFrPvcGroupMapIpObjectGroup
hwFrPvcGroupMapIpObjectGroup.description: The fr pvc-group mapping attribute group.

hwFrMapIpObjectGroup.name: hwFrMapIpObjectGroup
hwFrMapIpObjectGroup.description: The fr ip mapping attribute group.

hwFrMapPppObjectGroup.name: hwFrMapPppObjectGroup
hwFrMapPppObjectGroup.description: The fr ppp mapping attribute group.

hwFrMapBridgeObjectGroup.name: hwFrMapBridgeObjectGroup
hwFrMapBridgeObjectGroup.description: The fr bridge mapping attribute group.
